<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٥٩٠١ -<span class="c5"> ابن الشِّعِيري:</span> أحمد بن جعفر المقرئ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٥٩٠٢ -<span class="c5"> ابن الشفق:</span> أبو محمد عبد الوهاب بن عيسى بن الشفق المقرئ <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٥٩٠٣ -<span class="c5"> ابن شقر:</span> محمد بن عبد المنعم الحنفي <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٥٩٠٤ - ابن شقروة <span class="c2">(٧)</span>: عبيد الله <span class="c2">(٨)</span>،<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٥٩٠٥ - • وابنه الحسين <span class="c2">(٩)</span>،<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٥٩٠٦ - • وأخوه فضل الله <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>،<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
